Sankranti Special Telugu Devotional Songs 2026 | All Gods Bhakti Songs | Prosperity, Peace & Divine Blessings 


Celebrate the auspicious festival of Sankranti 2026 with this divine collection of All Gods Telugu Devotional Songs, dedicated to Lord Vishnu, Lord Shiva, Lord Venkateswara, Goddess Lakshmi, Durga Devi, Hanuman, Ganesha, Surya Bhagavan, Sai Baba, Ayyappa, and many more.

Sankranti symbolizes new beginnings, harvest, gratitude, and divine blessings.
Listening to Sankranti Special Bhakti Songs is believed to bring prosperity, happiness, good health, success, positive energy, and spiritual upliftment to the home and family.

Celebrate the auspicious Sankranti Festival 2026 with a divine collection of All Gods Kannada Devotional Songs, featuring powerful bhakti songs dedicated to Lord Shiva, Lord Vishnu, Lord Ganesha, Goddess Lakshmi, Lord Surya, and other deities.

Sankranti is a sacred harvest festival symbolizing new beginnings, prosperity, gratitude, and divine blessings.
Listening to Sankranti Special Bhakti Songs on this holy day is believed to remove obstacles, financial difficulties, negative energies, and bless devotees with health, wealth, happiness, peace, and success.

Presenting the official trailer of "Chowkidar", an intense action-drama that explores the thin line between duty and defiance. Starring the versatile Pruthvi Ambaar in a never-seen-before mass avatar and the 'Dialogue King' Sai Kumar in a powerful role, Chowkidar is set to be a cinematic feast for Kannada audiences.

Adding to the intensity is the brilliant Dhanya Ramkumar, with a soul-stirring background score and music by the sensation Sachin Basrur. Get ready for a story of grit, mystery, and raw power!

snippet.description:
Arijit gave us a special gift in 2026 with a brand new version of ‚ÄòSukoon‚Äô and some magical runs which you‚Äôve not heard before ‚ù§Ô∏è

Lyrics:
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 
Dil wohi sukoon dhoonde
Waisa hi qaraar maange 

Jo qudrat ne bikhere the
Bas meri raahon mein
Aur qismat ne sajaaye the
Meri nigaahon mein

Jaane ab kahaan milega 
Kahaan chhupa hoga 
Mil jaata toh rakh leta main
Apni panaahon mein

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Jhaank loon khud mein zara, sab kuch hai andar mere
Lehron pe milta nahin, jo gehre samandar mile 
Mehsoos hoga mujhe, jab khudko pehchanunga
Dil ke andar dekh kar, apni rooh ko jaanunga

Doobega‚Ä¶ Doobega‚Ä¶

Doobega toh tar jaaega
Har zarra mera
Varna tadap ke hi guzrega
Roz marra mera

Kya maine kabhi kiya hai
Thoda ishq bhi khudse 
Mil jaayega phir jo dhoondta hun 
Main darbadar kabse

Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai
Woh sukoon shayad mujhse hi hai
Mujh mein hi tha aur mujh mein hi hai

Woh sukoon mujhse hai‚Ä¶
Mujh mein hai sukoon‚Ä¶
